					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5520546#post-3744110</guid>
				<title>SCP-3719: Your Friendly Neighbourhood Lawnmower</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-5520546/scp-3719#post-3744110</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 20 Mar 2018 03:27:06 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Lt Flops</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1735419</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p><strong>SCP-3719:</strong> Your Friendly Neighbourhood Lawnmower<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735419&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Lt Flops" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735419)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lt-flops" >Lt Flops</a></span></p> </blockquote> <hr /> <p>Hi all, here’s my third SCP. This idea has been sitting in my head for about a year now, but I hadn't figured out how to write it until recently. My initial idea was to write a lawnmower that slowly degrades the bonds between neighbours. <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=776854&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Tanhony" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=776854)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tanhony" >Tanhony</a></span> gave me the alternate idea that it should form the bond between neighbours by <em>attaching them together physically</em>. Thanks to him for that!</p> <hr /> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▷&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Thanks&nbsp;and&nbsp;Image&nbsp;Attribution</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Special Thanks &#8212; Critters &amp; Beta Readers</strong></span></p> <p>▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2858989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Westrin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2858989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/westrin" >Westrin</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2199269&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Yossipossi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2199269)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yossipossi" >Yossipossi</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phamtomguy" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187915&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="PhamtomGuy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187915)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/phamtomguy" >PhamtomGuy</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/endingparadox" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3701955&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="EndingParadox" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3701955)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/endingparadox" >EndingParadox</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/optimisticlucio" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3199573&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="OptimisticLucio" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3199573)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/optimisticlucio" >OptimisticLucio</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mdvs" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2305422&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="mdvs" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2305422)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mdvs" >mdvs</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cambrian" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3400053&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Doctor Cambrian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3400053)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cambrian" >Doctor Cambrian</a></span><br /> ▷ <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601836982" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span></p> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:110%;"><strong>Image Attribution</strong></span></p> <blockquote> <p><strong>Filename:</strong> ecto-lawn-mower.jpg<br /> <strong>Name:</strong> lawn-mower-2293876<br /> <strong>Author:</strong> <a href="https://pixabay.com/users/alexas_fotos-686414/">Alexas_Fotos</a><br /> <strong>License:</strong> CC0 (Free for commercial use; No attribution required)<br /> <strong>Source Link:</strong> <a href="https://pixabay.com/images/id-2293876/">Pixabay</a></p> </blockquote> </div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">△&nbsp;Close</a></div> </div> </div> <hr /> <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:130%;"><strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/floppyphoenix">If you liked this, check out my Author Page!</a></strong></span></p> 
